Company Overview

							Citadel Advisory Group enjoys a reputation as one of the most trusted and respected mergers & acquisitions firms in the Energy Services arena. Our team of transaction, financial, and legal specialists provides investment banking services to middle market companies. Nothing gives us more satisfaction than helping business owners realize the full potential of their companies. We specialize in Energy Services, but we lend our expertise to other industries as well when we see that our expertise can benefit a client. Our services include:

							
Sell Side Representation including Divestitures and Management Buyouts
Corporate Finance: Capital Raisings, Restructurings, Majority or Minority Recapitalizations
Strategic, Growth or Exit Planning Consultation 
Buy Side Representation

 Our clients generally consist of both privately-held and public companies across the country looking for specific strategic acquisitions, divestitures, or growth capital. We welcome the opportunity to discuss your situation, and work with you to achieve your goals. Please contact us for a confidential, complimentary discussion.



